Crispy Chicken Burger with Avocado Salsa

35 min
$12.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 25%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dietary Tags:

high-proteinlow-carb

Description

A crispy chicken burger topped with creamy avocado salsa, perfect for a quick and delicious meal.

Ingredients
